    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The remaining 6 factors are appropriately scoped at Gradation 1 and are satisfied through documented qualitative evidence consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 was confirmed across all 5 operating points.",
